Package: tdaunif
Title: Uniform manifold samplers for topological data analysis
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jason Cory", "Brunson", email = "cornelioid@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Brandon", "Demkowicz", email = "brandondemkowicz@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Sanmati", "Choudhary", email = "20choudharysa@fpsct.org", role = "aut")
    )
Description: This package contains functions that generate uniform random
    samples from simple manifolds, optionally with noise, which are commonly
    used to test topological data analytic (TDA) techniques.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    testthat,
    vdiffr (>= 0.2)
